file.name: issue_918.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: headers in components
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /2.0/users/:
    get:
      operationId: getUserByName
      responses:
        '200':
          description: The User
          headers:
            X-Rate-Limit:
              $ref: "#/components/headers/X-Rate-Limit-Ref"
components:
  headers:
    X-Rate-Limit-Ref:
      description: The number of allowed requests in the current period
      schema:
        type: integer
